Description.name: Located in Jumeirah Beach, Dubai Marine Beach Resort &amp; Spa is a perfect starting point from which to

Located in Jumeirah Beach, Dubai Marine Beach Resort &amp; Spa is a perfect starting point from which to explore Dubai.&lt;br&gt; Featuring a complete list of amenities, guests will find their stay at the property a comfortable one.&lt;br&gt; All the necessary facilities, including 24-hour room service, free Wi-Fi in all rooms, 24-hour security, 24-hour front desk, facilities for disabled guests, are at hand.&lt;br&gt; Some of the well-appointed guestrooms feature television LCD/plasma screen, carpeting, separate living room, whirlpool bathtub, non smoking rooms.&lt;br&gt; Recuperate from a full day of sightseeing in the comfort of your room or take advantage of the hotel&apos;s recreational facilities, including private beach, fitness center, sauna, outdoor pool, spa.&lt;br&gt; Convenience and comfort makes Dubai Marine Beach Resort &amp; Spa the perfect choice for your stay in Dubai.&lt;br&gt;

&lt;strong&gt;Others&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;p&gt;A tourism tax will be charged directly at the property.,American Express, Visa, Euro/Mastercard, Diners Club,The Kid&apos;s Club is permanently closed.&lt;br&gt;
